metadata.description: We Are Eternal Spirits (WAES) is a NFT project that invites you to explore the Eternal Spirits. The collection consists of 10,000 unique Spirits that are your companion. By owning a WAES NFT, you become a part of the WASD community and gain benefits with it. Join the WASD community and unlock the potential of the Eternal Spirits.
metadata.name: Essence Ashes #1
